$G$ Toys:<br>Toys are used to increase happiness of a pet. They have a set amount of durability, once this durability is reduced to zero the toy is consumed. #
$B$ BouncyBall - A little rubber bouncy ball. #
$F$ Football - A size 5 football, pumped and ready. #
$L$ Laser - Battery powered laser pointer. #
$M$ Mirror - A regular mirror, is it really a toy? #
$R$ Radio - A radio capable of picking up both FM and AM frequencies. #
$W$ RunningWheel - Like a hamster wheel only comes in all different sizes. #
$T$ TV - Television with inbuilt Freeview. #